    {
      "instruction": "<p>Peel and finely dice your<strong> red onion[s]</strong></p><p>Cut your <strong>red chilli[es]</strong><span class=\"text-danger\"> </span>in half lengthways, deseed (scrape the seeds out with a teaspoon) and chop finely</p><p>Peel and finely chop (or grate) your <strong>garlic</strong></p>",
