    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the sauce is thickening, chop your <strong>basa fillet[s]</strong> into bite-sized pieces</p><p>Add the <strong>chopped basa </strong>to the<strong> </strong>sauce and give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>peri-peri</strong> <strong>basa pie filling</strong></p>",
