    {
      "instruction": "<p>Transfer the <strong>peri-peri basa pie filling</strong> to an <strong>oven-proof dish</strong> and top with the <strong>potato discs </strong>– this is your<strong> potato-topped peri-peri basa pie</strong></p><p>Put the dish in the oven for 15-20 min or until the fish is cooked through and the pie is bubbling and golden</p><p>Tip: Your fish is cooked once it turns opaque and flakes easily</p>",
